item.title: Welcome to my website!
item.description: Hey all! Welcome to my new website! Its been awhile since i’ve posted on a blog(Myspace/Xanga days!). This is sort of a blog documenting my PhD progress while also subltly mixing in aspects of my social life. I’ll try to update this frequently.
